# Crime Scenes

This is where the real gameplay happens.

Every crime scene is handcrafted.

No random hidden-object gameplay.

Instead players investigate like a real detective.

Examples:

Photograph evidence.

Collect fingerprints.

Collect DNA.

Interview witnesses.

Analyze footprints.

Measure blood spatter.

Inspect broken locks.

Read financial records.

Recover deleted files.

Reconstruct timelines.

Compare conflicting statements.

Crack codes.

Study CCTV.

Analyze phone data.

Every investigation feels like solving a movie.

---

# Missions

Every promotion contains 10 carefully designed missions.

Each mission:

Feels cinematic.

Contains multiple suspects.

Contains twists.

Requires thinking.

Has optional evidence.

Has multiple puzzle types.

Gets progressively harder.

Mission 10 is always the "boss case" of that promotion.

